locality: S facing slope N of the Govermental house of Gosainkund.

Tampe-la. Wangchuck Centennial Park. BT-TPL-SMC. Collectors included: Sangay Dema, Richen Yangzon, Tshering Dorji, Tshering Wangmo, Richen Dorji, Jigme Wangchuck, Suresh K. Ghimire, Katie Konchar, & Jan Salick.
